---
title: Bulgogi-Flavored Pulled Pork Sandwiches with Sriracha Mayo & Pickled Veggie Slaw
description: It’s tough to resist the saucy, tender texture and tangy flavor of pulled pork. Here, it stars in sandwiches that come together in just 15 minutes. For this lightning-speed meal, you’ll mix your slaw, warm your pulled pork with a bulgogi-flavored sauce, and pile it all onto toasted brioche buns. Just think: you’re that much closer to sandwich bliss.
